== 旅程 ==
[[File:WDWRR_-_Fantasyland_Station.jpg|链接=https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:WDWRR_-_Fantasyland_Station.jpg]]
火车从魔法王国公园入口旁的美国大街站出发，沿单轨顺时针方向在环形路线上行驶。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Magic Kingdom and Fun Facts|url=http://www.wdwradio.com/2007/09/magic-kingdom-and-fun-facts/|accessdate=2016-06-19|author=Mongello|date=2007-09-14|first=Lou|work=WDWRadio|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120109234108/http://www.wdwradio.com/2007/09/magic-kingdom-and-fun-facts/|archivedate=2012-01-09}}</ref>每列火车往返全程大致需要20分钟，每天都会有二至三列火车运行，通常每天有两列火车运行。<ref name="Leaphart2016pp166–167">{{Harvp|Leaphart|2016}}.</ref><ref name="WaltDisneyWorldForGrownups">{{Cite web|title=Take A Break On The Walt Disney World Railroad|url=http://www.wdwforgrownups.com/articles/take-break-walt-disney-world-railroad|accessdate=2017-04-12|author=Kirk|date=2015-10-06|first=Kristen|work=Walt Disney World For Grownups|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151009012216/http://www.wdwforgrownups.com/articles/take-break-walt-disney-world-railroad|archivedate=2015-10-09}}</ref>每列火车都配备一名工程师和一名消防队员，以及负责引导乘客的列车长。<ref>{{Cite web|title=The Quick 10: 10 Magic Kingdom Attractions and Their Secrets|url=http://mentalfloss.com/article/19741/quick-10-10-magic-kingdom-attractions-and-their-secrets|accessdate=2016-06-19|author=Conradt|date=2008-10-01|first=Stacy|work=[[Mental_Floss|Mental Floss]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151101034515/http://mentalfloss.com/article/19741/quick-10-10-magic-kingdom-attractions-and-their-secrets|archivedate=2015-11-01}}</ref><ref name="Trains">{{Cite magazine|last=Withers|first=Bob|date=January 2010|title=This Is a Mickey Mouse Railroad!|url=http://trn.trains.com/~/media/files/pdf/web-exclusives/trn-i0110.pdf|magazine=[[Trains_(magazine)|Trains]]|publisher=[[Kalmbach_Media|Kalmbach Publishing]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161008211020/http://trn.trains.com/~/media/files/pdf/web-exclusives/trn-i0110.pdf|archive-date=2016-10-08|access-date=2017-05-19}}</ref>{{Rp|4–5}}

火车离开美国大街站后，乘客们可以看到[[探險世界|探险世界]]，在跨过一座小桥，穿过一条小隧道后，就到了边域世界。 <ref name="Leaphart2016pp154–157">{{Harvp|Leaphart|2016}}.</ref> 在穿过飞溅山的隧道后，火车在第二个站点边域世界站停靠。  <ref>{{Cite web|title=Disney from the Twenty-Something: "Walt Disney World Railroad"|url=http://www.wdwradio.com/2014/07/disney-twenty-something-walt-disney-world-railroad/|accessdate=2019-03-09|author=Corsello|date=2014-07-07|first=Caitlin|work=WDWRadio|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190301181813/http://www.wdwradio.com/2014/07/disney-twenty-something-walt-disney-world-railroad/|archivedate=2019-03-01}}</ref>

稍作停留，火车继续出发。沿途可以看到雷霆山过山车，翻过一座多功能移动桥。移动桥凌驾于连接美国之河和[[旱塢|干船坞]]的运河之上。 <ref name="Leaphart2016pp158–159">{{Harvp|Leaphart|2016}}.</ref> <ref name="Korkis2016p4">{{Harvp|Korkis|2016}}.</ref> 这座桥最早属于佛罗里达东海岸铁路公司。 <ref name="Leaphart2016pp148–149">{{Harvp|Leaphart|2016}}.</ref> 接着，乘客们将会看到模拟[[美國原住民|美洲原住民]]和野生动物生活状态的展示区。 <ref>{{Cite web|title=Celebrate 40th Birthday of Walt Disney's Magic Kingdom (and Check Out These 'Secret' Spots)|url=http://www.tampabay.com/features/travel/florida/celebrate-40th-birthday-of-walt-disneys-magic-kingdom-and-check-out-these/1194073|accessdate=2016-06-19|author=Daly|date=2011-09-28|first=Sean|work=[[Tampa_Bay_Times|Tampa Bay Times]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130731010226/http://www.tampabay.com/features/travel/florida/celebrate-40th-birthday-of-walt-disneys-magic-kingdom-and-check-out-these/1194073|archivedate=2013-07-31}}</ref> <ref name="OCRegister">{{Cite web|title=A Former Disney Imagineer’s Guide to Walt Disney World’s Frontierland|url=https://www.ocregister.com/2017/05/17/a-former-disney-imagineers-guide-to-walt-disney-worlds-frontierland/|accessdate=2019-03-13|author=Eades|date=2017-05-17|first=Mark|work=[[Orange_County_Register|Orange County Register]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20181212005139/https://www.ocregister.com/2017/05/17/a-former-disney-imagineers-guide-to-walt-disney-worlds-frontierland/|archivedate=2018-12-12}}</ref>火车从[[架空道路|天桥]]下通过后，穿过通往火车[[机务段|机务]]处的[[铁路支线|支线]]，到达下一个站点——幻想世界站。 <ref name="HuffingtonPost">{{Cite web|title=How Walt Disney's Love of Trains Changed the World|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/rich-grant/how-walt-disneys-love-of-trains-changed-the-world_b_6894946.html|accessdate=2016-06-19|author=Grant|date=2015-03-18|first=Rich|work=[[HuffPost|HuffPost]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160318033725/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/rich-grant/how-walt-disneys-love-of-trains-changed-the-world_b_6894946.html|archivedate=2016-03-18}}</ref>  <ref name="Leaphart2016pp160–161">{{Harvp|Leaphart|2016}}.</ref>

再次离站后，火车爬升2％的斜坡，乘客们置身于明日世界，经过太空山过山车，翻过一座小桥，回到美国大街站。 <ref name="Trains">{{Cite magazine|last=Withers|first=Bob|date=January 2010|title=This Is a Mickey Mouse Railroad!|url=http://trn.trains.com/~/media/files/pdf/web-exclusives/trn-i0110.pdf|magazine=[[Trains_(magazine)|Trains]]|publisher=[[Kalmbach_Media|Kalmbach Publishing]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161008211020/http://trn.trains.com/~/media/files/pdf/web-exclusives/trn-i0110.pdf|archive-date=2016-10-08|access-date=2017-05-19}}</ref> {{Rp|4}} <ref name="Leaphart2016pp162–165">{{Harvp|Leaphart|2016}}.</ref>这就是园区''的大环游''。 <ref>{{Cite web|title=Walt Disney World Railroad|url=http://www.themeparkinsider.com/reviews/walt_disney_world's_magic_kingdom/walt_disney_world_railroad/|accessdate=2016-06-19|author=|date=2013-12-12|first=|work=Theme Park Insider|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150905111049/http://www.themeparkinsider.com/reviews/walt_disney_world%27s_magic_kingdom/walt_disney_world_railroad/|archivedate=2015-09-05}}</ref><gallery mode="packed" caption="迪士尼世界铁路站点">
