</gallery>由于轨道靠近烟花燃放区，因此在烟花表演期间火车不运行。 <ref name="WaltDisneyWorldForGrownups">{{Cite web|title=Take A Break On The Walt Disney World Railroad|url=http://www.wdwforgrownups.com/articles/take-break-walt-disney-world-railroad|accessdate=2017-04-12|author=Kirk|date=2015-10-06|first=Kristen|work=Walt Disney World For Grownups|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151009012216/http://www.wdwforgrownups.com/articles/take-break-walt-disney-world-railroad|archivedate=2015-10-09}}</ref> 另外，从1999年开始，每天会有一场单独定价的巡回演出，命名为''迪士尼的“我们的蒸汽火车背后的魔法”'' ，乘客们可以借机参观机车库。 <ref name="HuffingtonPost">{{Cite web|title=How Walt Disney's Love of Trains Changed the World|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/rich-grant/how-walt-disneys-love-of-trains-changed-the-world_b_6894946.html|accessdate=2016-06-19|author=Grant|date=2015-03-18|first=Rich|work=[[HuffPost|HuffPost]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160318033725/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/rich-grant/how-walt-disneys-love-of-trains-changed-the-world_b_6894946.html|archivedate=2016-03-18}}</ref> <ref name="Trains">{{Cite magazine|last=Withers|first=Bob|date=January 2010|title=This Is a Mickey Mouse Railroad!|url=http://trn.trains.com/~/media/files/pdf/web-exclusives/trn-i0110.pdf|magazine=[[Trains_(magazine)|Trains]]|publisher=[[Kalmbach_Media|Kalmbach Publishing]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161008211020/http://trn.trains.com/~/media/files/pdf/web-exclusives/trn-i0110.pdf|archive-date=2016-10-08|access-date=2017-05-19}}</ref> {{Rp|2}} <ref>{{Cite web|title=Disney's The Magic Behind Our Steam Trains Tour – official website|url=https://disneyworld.disney.go.com/events-tours/magic-kingdom/magic-behind-steam-trains-tour/|accessdate=2016-06-25|author=|date=|first=|publisher=[[Disney_Parks,_Experiences_and_Products#Walt_Disney_Parks_and_Resorts|Walt Disney Parks and Resorts]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160322073650/https://disneyworld.disney.go.com/events-tours/magic-kingdom/magic-behind-steam-trains-tour/|archivedate=2016-03-22}}</ref>

== 机动车组 ==
[[File:WDWRR_-_WDW_Monorail_3.jpg|替代=The back of a locomotive tender with the inside of the locomotive's cab partially visible]]
在这条线上工作时，每辆火车每小时消耗95升的燃料和760升的水，而每辆消防车可以容纳2510升的燃料和6950升的水。<ref name="Broggie2014p333">{{Harvp|Broggie|2014}}.</ref><ref name="Broggie2014pp393–394">{{Harvp|Broggie|2014}}.</ref>以前，这四辆火车头都在北卡罗来纳州吹风岩的铁路公司检修。<ref name="Trains">{{Cite magazine|last=Withers|first=Bob|date=January 2010|title=This Is a Mickey Mouse Railroad!|url=http://trn.trains.com/~/media/files/pdf/web-exclusives/trn-i0110.pdf|magazine=[[Trains_(magazine)|Trains]]|publisher=[[Kalmbach_Media|Kalmbach Publishing]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161008211020/http://trn.trains.com/~/media/files/pdf/web-exclusives/trn-i0110.pdf|archive-date=2016-10-08|access-date=2017-05-19}}</ref>{{Rp|5}}四辆火车头各牵引五节车厢，每节车厢，每节车厢可容纳75名乘客，因此，每列火车总共可容纳375名乘客。<ref name="Broggie2014p331">{{Harvp|Broggie|2014}}.</ref>车头背面的蒸汽发电机为机车和客车供电。<ref name="Leaphart2016p197">{{Harvp|Leaphart|2016}}.</ref>火车头没有刹车，但客车有刹车。{{Rp|5}}{{Clear}}

== 信号灯 ==
[[File:WDWRR_-_Frontierland_Station_Block_Signal_Light.jpg|链接=https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:WDWRR_-_Frontierland_Station_Block_Signal_Light.jpg]]
火车上的工程师，消防员和列车长可以通过[[自动闭塞|信号灯]]判断铁路干道是否畅通无阻。 <ref name="HuffingtonPost">{{Cite web|title=How Walt Disney's Love of Trains Changed the World|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/rich-grant/how-walt-disneys-love-of-trains-changed-the-world_b_6894946.html|accessdate=2016-06-19|author=Grant|date=2015-03-18|first=Rich|work=[[HuffPost|HuffPost]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160318033725/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/rich-grant/how-walt-disneys-love-of-trains-changed-the-world_b_6894946.html|archivedate=2016-03-18}}</ref> <ref name="Leaphart2016pp166–167">{{Harvp|Leaphart|2016}}.</ref> <ref name="Trains">{{Cite magazine|last=Withers|first=Bob|date=January 2010|title=This Is a Mickey Mouse Railroad!|url=http://trn.trains.com/~/media/files/pdf/web-exclusives/trn-i0110.pdf|magazine=[[Trains_(magazine)|Trains]]|publisher=[[Kalmbach_Media|Kalmbach Publishing]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161008211020/http://trn.trains.com/~/media/files/pdf/web-exclusives/trn-i0110.pdf|archive-date=2016-10-08|access-date=2017-05-19}}</ref> {{Rp|5}} 另外，当霹雳过山车轨道在传送列车上下的时候，其转换轨道会在铁路轨道上方摇摆，这时，铁路人员也可以通过信号灯判断道况。  迪士尼世界铁路轨道分为七段，每段轨道旁都有一个信号灯。  <ref name="Leaphart2016p152">{{Harvp|Leaphart|2016}}.</ref> 分别在三个站点，站点之间的三段主干线旁以及连接主干线和机车库的支线旁都分别设有信号灯。  

